OL,3,CCalls to improve 'chaotic' junction
OL,4,Cthat is 'an accident waiting to happen'
OL,6,FITV News' Sam Blackledge spoke to
OL,7,Fresidents and traders in Plymouth
OL,9,FPeople in a busy area of Plymouth are
OL,10,Fcalling for a safer pedestrian
OL,11,Fcrossing, describing one junction in
OL,12,Fparticular as "chaotic".
OL,14,FThe junction of Mutley Plain and
OL,15,FGreenbank Road has been described as
OL,16,F"an accident waiting to happen".
