OL,3,CCalls to improve 'chaotic' junction
OL,4,Cthat is 'an accident waiting to happen'
OL,6,FNick Lear, Minister at Mutley Baptist
OL,7,FChurch, said: "The problem is that not
OL,8,Fall of the traffic flow is controlled,
OL,9,Fso sometimes you've got to try to
OL,10,Fcross the road and watch for three
OL,11,Fdifferent traffic streams at different
OL,12,Fstages, none of which are stopped
OL,13,Fspecifically for you.
OL,15,F"You have to just keep your eyes on
OL,16,Fthe swivel all the time, when it could
OL,17,Fbe so much easier and so much simpler."
OL,19,FLocal politicians have set up a
OL,20,Fpetition calling for a safer
OL,21,Fpedestrian crossing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
