OL,3,CCalls to improve 'chaotic' junction
OL,4,Cthat is 'an accident waiting to happen'
OL,6,FLabour MP Luke Pollard said: "It's an
OL,7,Faccident waiting to happen because you
OL,8,Fcan't see the traffic coming towards
OL,9,Fyou due to the tight bends, there's no
OL,10,Findication for pedestrians when it's
OL,11,Fsafe to cross, and people rush across
OL,12,Fand this is really a dangerous spot.
OL,14,FCharlotte Holloway, Labour councillor
OL,15,Ffor Drake ward, said: "I think there
OL,16,Fare a number of options, I want to
OL,17,Ftalk to the experts at the council to
OL,18,Fsee what solutions are going to fit
OL,19,Fhere whilst maintaining the smooth
OL,20,Fflow of traffic.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
