OL,6,F"I think a pedestrian crossing with a
OL,7,Fbutton of some kind is an option,
OL,8,Fthere need to be clear windows when
OL,9,Fit's safe to walk and not safe to walk
OL,10,Fso pedestrians and drivers alike know
OL,11,Fthat the road is safe."
OL,13,FA spokesman for Plymouth City Council
OL,14,Fsaid they are aware of the concerns
OL,15,Fand looking into the costs of
OL,16,Fimproving the crossing.
